  <section class="widget text-4 widget_text">
   <div class="widget-inner">
    <h3>
     Supporting Graduate Education
    </h3>
    <div class="textwidget">
     Donors to graduate education at UC Berkeley are investors in the promise and potential of our graduate student community – in the proven capacity of our students to advance every professional field, and to discover new knowledge that illuminates the world for the greater good.
    </div>
   </div>
